  "body": "<p>It's truly pregnancy brain when you turn to a friend and tell them you are stuck on an assignment for scrapbooking milestones. Without skipping a beat, she simply said, “how about your pregnancy?”. And then we went on to giggle about the whole thing. Here is how my Milestones layout came together. I started off with putting down a thin layer of gesso using a foam brush from side to side. After drying, I added some splatters.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/4ee78cf86c7ab340.jpg?v=1782533589\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I placed the photos down (without adhering them) for planning the rest of the page.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/718c4797db0edbde.jpg?v=1782533591\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"2c-DSC_0030-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/39b7b757ef785854.jpg?v=1782533594\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"2j-DSC_0040-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/b8ace5181ddb9956.jpg?v=1782533597\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"2d-DSC_0031-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/051660b1b1baef7f.jpg?v=1782533600\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2e-DSC_0032-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/ce986f90c7d653af.jpg?v=1782533603\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2f-DSC_0035-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/7bdb21e44fcb8707.jpg?v=1782533606\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2g-DSC_0036-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/a107ad13304631fb.jpg?v=1782533609\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2h-DSC_0038-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/d9b34756ab9236b3.jpg?v=1782533612\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2i-DSC_0039-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/592ab45be19121a6.jpg?v=1782533614\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Final touch was some chevron stitching using our <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/139091-capture-yes-please-amy-tangerine-embroidery-stencil-kit/%3Fsource_type%3DLAY%26source_id%3D1919612\">Capture embroidery stencil kit</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"2k-hello-bump2-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/8091b6117e7360c6.jpg?v=1782533617\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2l-hello-bump.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/bd79245dd4f588cc.jpg?v=1782533620\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Hello Bump | Copyright Two Peas In A BucketComplete supply list can be found at Two Peas In A Bucket.</p>"
